      <div class="view-content">
          <div class="views-row"><div class="views-field views-field-field-blog-category"><div class="field-content field-name-field-blog-category"><a href="/blog-categories/interviews" hreflang="en">Interviews</a>
</div></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-thumbnail"><div class="field-content imageleft">  <a href="/blog/interviews/not-knowing-how-get-there-what-makes-you-great-conversation-chilean-poet-mario" hreflang="en"><img loading="lazy" src="/sites/worldliteraturetoday.org/files/styles/blog_thumbnail/public/Melendez-anchor.jpg?itok=zF8htIzy" width="100" height="75" alt="A photograph of Mario Meléndez" typeof="foaf:Image" class="img-fluid image-style-blog-thumbnail" />

</a>

</div></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-richtitle"><h4 class="field-content"><a href="https://www.worldliteraturetoday.org/blog/interviews/not-knowing-how-get-there-what-makes-you-great-conversation-chilean-poet-mario">“Not Knowing How to Get There Is What Makes You Great”: A Conversation with Chilean Poet Mario Meléndez
</a>
</h4></div><div><div class="blog-summary">Mario Meléndez / Photo by Marco UgarteRegarded as one of the most original voices of the new Latin American poetry, Mario Meléndez (b. 1971) is a…
</div></div><span class="views-field views-field-field-date"><span class="field-content date-display-single">January 23, 2025
</span></span>|<span><span class="field-name-field-blogauthor"><a href="/author/ming-di" hreflang="en">Ming Di</a>
</span></span></div>
    <div class="views-row"><div class="views-field views-field-field-blog-category"><div class="field-content field-name-field-blog-category"><a href="/blog-categories/book-reviews" hreflang="en">Book Reviews</a>
</div></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-thumbnail"><div class="field-content imageleft">  <a href="/blog/book-reviews/poetry-way-life-conversations-lenard-d-moore-miho-kinnas" hreflang="en"><img loading="lazy" src="/sites/worldliteraturetoday.org/files/styles/blog_thumbnail/public/Lenard-w.jpg?itok=gB5eolkt" width="100" height="75" alt="A photograph of Lenard Moore" typeof="foaf:Image" class="img-fluid image-style-blog-thumbnail" />

</a>

</div></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-richtitle"><h4 class="field-content"><a href="https://www.worldliteraturetoday.org/blog/book-reviews/poetry-way-life-conversations-lenard-d-moore-miho-kinnas">Poetry as a Way of Life: <em>Conversations with Lenard D. Moore</em>
</a>
</h4></div><div><div class="blog-summary">Edited by John Zheng, <em>Conversations with Lenard D. Moore</em> (University Press of Mississippi, 2024) collects sixteen interviews conducted over…
